txt.en: 'Now that the road to Nurn is blocked, our food supply is running low.\n\n'Steal some of his provisions for us.'
A guard spotted you sneaking around!
Steal food from Fushaum Bal North ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
'Ah this food will continue feeding us for quite some time!'
Food can be found in Fushaum Bal North.\n\nYou should steal food from Fushaum Bal North while avoiding the guards.
The Haradrim Commander can be found at Fushaum Bal South.\n\nYou should talk to the Haradrim Commander.
<rgb=#FF0000>Don't let the Fushaum Guards spot you</rgb>
The encampment of Fushaum Bal is a lawless home to evil men once under the command of Sauron.
